original_title: Shaquille O'Neal All-Star Comedy Jam Live from Atlanta
overview: Shaquille O'Neal presents funnyman and actor Faizon Love as he takes on hosting duties for the latest installment of ALL-STAR COMEDY JAM. This time around, NBA All-Star and celebrity personality Shaquille O'Neal has handpicked some of stand-up comedy's funniest up-and-coming talents and paired them with veterans of the comedy stage.
title: Shaquille O'Neal All-Star Comedy Jam Live from Atlanta
